✅ CORS hota kya hai?
CORS ek security feature hai jo web browsers implement karte hain. Yeh prevent karta hai ki ek website doosri website ke backend se bina permission ke request na bhej sake.

Example lo:

Backend run ho raha hai → http://localhost:8000
Frontend run ho raha hai → http://localhost:3000
Agar frontend backend se request karega, toh browser CORS error de sakta hai kyunki dono different origins hain.


