----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
monggose 
Mongoose ek Object Data Modeling (ODM) library hai jo MongoDB ke saath kaam karti hai. Jab hum MongoDB ko directly use karte hain, toh humein manual queries likhni padti hain aur data validation bhi manually handle karna padta hai. Mongoose isse simple aur efficient bana deta hai.
